Package edu.ncsu.csc.CoffeeMaker.models

Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc.CoffeeMaker.models.DomainObject
      • edu.ncsu.csc.CoffeeMaker.models.User
  • @Entity
public class User
extends DomainObject
    Abstract class representing a User in the CoffeeMaker system. This class is a shared type that is used for all users of the CoffeeMaker system and handles basic functionality such as authenticating the user in the system.
    Author:
    Ellie Murphy
